715549f-a.title: Manhattan: 131st Street (West) - Old Broadway
715549f-a.text:
West 13lst Street, at, adjoining and east of the
S.E. corner of Old Broadway (right) as viewed westward.
No. 538 is a two story Trane house separating the
corner property (No. 67 Old Broadway) from the stone
garage (No. 536 West 131st Street). At the right margin
appears a portion of the old frame building at the S.W.
corner, bearing No's. o6 Old Broadway and 5722 West 13lst
Street.
View No. 2 is limited and shows solely No. 538, the
frane dwelling aforementioned.
View 1: April 1, 1938
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
J. Clarence Davies Collection
Museum of The City of New York
Neg. No. 318
CREDIT LINNE ILPERATIVE  View 2: 1932
